# Place TLS certificate files here:
#   fullchain.pem
#   privkey.pem
#
# Source options:
#   - Let's Encrypt via certbot --webroot (mount /var/www/certbot)
#   - Cloudflare Origin Certificate (free, valid 15y, only if you front
#     the site with Cloudflare)
#   - Self-signed for staging only (openssl req ...)
#
# This file exists only so the directory is tracked in git.
